{"tid":834584,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"娶唔娶到老婆就睇今晚","createTime":"2018-09-24T09:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T10:42:06.000Z","uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"65ede5e42ffd6d8bee15ac3c4e3b4e5b93895f74","tid":834584,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"冇，是咁的。為左避免將來成為大魔法師<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，小弟準備今晚博一博，<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 落樓下公園物色定一個靚女，等佢大個可以做我老婆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁為左吸引佢既注意，同埋想令佢采我，所以我準備送份禮物俾佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n預計到個對話會係咁：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我    <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：未來老婆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我：咦，小妹妹你一個人係度玩呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老婆：係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？哥哥你想做咩呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「冇，我想送碌棍俾你玩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以想請教下巴打，瑩光棒幾錢支？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0b4676047b02b53c2c96fc518293e0a62acb9c","tid":834584,"uid":56444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f72f4d92e42e62548c5beb6e4e5ce398133dbb","tid":834584,"uid":92951,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/174006_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F174006_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a6c0fec2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a530b0010d4259705863260c7b4ff4f90d1e75c","tid":834584,"uid":88284,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"遊蕩罪<br />\n根據 第200章《刑事罪行條例》 第160(1)條 ，任何人如在建築物的共用部份遊蕩，意圖干犯可被逮捕的罪行，可處罰款10,000元和監禁六個月。"},{"pid":"1ea107c620e437d7543cc46ba8f0cfd1fbb3534d","tid":834584,"uid":38465,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b3d9ba64edc9db7fcae28d4db850e8aa83da98","tid":834584,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951ba0d20ffda5a25b3d426c5d852223948a69ec","tid":834584,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360dcbe049f3e4e5e14a9fbdc32b2c84316f76a5","tid":834584,"uid":16624,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"入監倉做人老婆就得"},{"pid":"8d15df1c42772c9c293560f6a23d725423235c6f","tid":834584,"uid":203365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:42:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">FBI</span></span>"},{"pid":"99e15e896e3d1e814e14a5591c373ae2de48f2b2","tid":834584,"uid":46135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:54:07.